title: Batman Beyond vol 5 (2012-2013) Complete
description:
Complete vol 5 of the Batman Beyond comic series, issues 1-29. This contains only the digitally published Batman Beyond segments, NOT the complete Batman Beyond Unlimited books which also contain adventures with the Justice League.

The story is continued in the rebranded and renumbered Batman Beyond 2.0, so keep an eye out for those titles.

Please seed for the enjoyment of all!
